      "id": "PopularPost83021",
      "post_content": "Re comments below: Casting this and then [Kaervek's Spite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kaervek's Spite ) in response isn't quite as bad a trick as it sounds. You get 5 life loss *plus* all the normal effects of this *plus* you untap all your land. So it's roughly equivalent to the mechanic of spells like [Rewind](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rewind ) or [Great Whale](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Great Whale)... but more so.",
      "posted_by": "nibelheim_valesti",
